IPK project 2 - packet sniffer
catch, identify and dump network packets

------

Compilation:
make

Help:
./ipk-sniffer -h
or
./ipk-sniffer --help

Run (list available interfaces):
./ipk-sniffer -i

Run (catch one packet, any device, any port, any protocol):
./ipk-sniffer

------

List of submitted files:
src/
src/main.cpp
src/config.h
src/sniffer.h
src/config.cpp
src/sniffer.cpp
Makefile
README
manual.pdf
